HELLO!
We are Yuval Fishman and Erel Nahum and this is our Boggle.

Cool Features:
    1) top tier design - we designed a custom logo and created a beautiful starting page
        the opens before the game begins.

    2) dragging instead of clicking - tired of clicking? no more! with the assistant
        of '<B1-Motion>' feature of tkinter you can now drag of curser over the screen
        and play quicker and enjoy more.

    3) Touch screen support - we both have touch screen laptops and decided that it'll
        be super cool if our game supports touch gestures.

We hope you'll enjoy our game!
Erel Nahum & Yuval Fishman